title: Dallas 10x12 Something Old, Something New.avi
description:
Yes boys and girls: DALLAS is back, and now that the dream is over, its even better than ever!

Bobby returns to Jock's crash site to seek evidence to disprove Wes' claim; J.R., warned by the CIA, tries to disassociate himself from B.D. Calhoun; Donna's lobbying in Washington continues; Miss Ellie remains undecided on Wes.

First Aired: 12/5/1986

Dack Rambo (Jack) is not present in this episode.



Note: I am happy to inform you that I have obtained all the episodes of s10 and will post them here during this month
